Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}其实早已崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}别来烦扰我  Craze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:49.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}坚持自我  即使四面楚歌  yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}身处起点时就已危机四伏
